2004-10-11  James Gallagher  <jimg@zoey.opendap.org>

	* FilterDirHTML.pm:
	Fixed anchor_ref --> anchor_href in one of the debug statments.

	* FilterDirHTML.pm:
	Hacked up the comments so the code is easier to read. Added a note about bug
	755 and bug 814.

	* DODS_Dispatch.pm, FilterDirHTML.pm:
	Added changes from NRL. These address a problem with the directory
	response and files whose type (HDF, netCDF, et c.) are determined using
	a regex that looks at the complete path and not just the filename. The
	problem was that the full path was not used when building the directory
	listing which meant that files that should have been treated as data files
	were not.
	The patches were provided by Brandon Casey <casey@hydrogen.nrlssc.navy.mil>.

	* DODS_Dispatch.pm:
	Incorporated a patch from John Allision that fixes a problem he had with the
	version and .ver responses. See bug 820.

	* DODS_Dispatch.pm:
	Fixed a spelling mistake in one of the error messages.

